title: Twosday Manifesting
itunes:title: Twosday Manifesting
description:
Today on the show we opened up the phone lines to see what our listeners thought about the recent Tinder Swindle doc and the CEO comments following the documentary. Moreover, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a daycare company after employees left a 2-year-old daughter alone inside before the parent came, so we opened the phone lines to see how our listeners would react if that happened to their child.
